Package: plotstudio
Type: Package
Title: Plot Studio
Version: 2.9.17
Author: Torry Scott Dennis, PhD
Maintainer: Torry Scott Dennis, PhD <tsdennis@smcm.edu>
Description: An interactive statistical graph-building module for jamovi with
    analyses for distributions, categorical frequencies, between-subjects
    comparisons, repeated measures, scatterplots, correlation matrices, and
    Likert survey items, plus a chart-selection guide. Provides click-to-edit
    styling, module-aware statistics, fuzzy setting search, accessibility
    checks, annotations, reusable palettes and styles, and SVG, PDF, PNG, and
    JPG export.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: jmvcore (>= 0.8.5), R6, htmltools, jsonlite
Suggests: rsvg, MASS
